➜中国好人汪太银咏妇女节快乐
http://www.sohu.com/a/299999042_528362	44814
<p class="ql-align-justify">春风吹柳吐絮花，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">巾帼飘扬迎彩霞。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">良母舵起半边天，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">仁爱无边兴中华。</p>
